{"type": "article", "id": 2580, "title": "极具工业设计感的帽子", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-26T08:13:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232246ytUHKWnAfdN062qe.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t在今年的伦敦设计节上，英国设计师 Julia Georgallis 与德国设计师 Dustin Jessen 在伦敦皇家艺术学院（ RCA )的 Big Small 展览上，带来了一系列反潮流的帽子，受传统制帽技术的启发，这个系列的帽子造型惊人地简单，散发出十足的工业设计感。这一系列的帽子提供黑色、绿黄色、蓝色以及海军蓝 4 色可选，定价 80 英镑，<a href=\"http://industrialfashion.bigcartel.com/category/hats\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232244fnqgOzGkHw42deZr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232245E68TKLDIqOdFxMma.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232245KzOoYZSRNxg3Xkrc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}